To select text, use any of the //move// keypresses shown above while
holding down the ~KShift~E key. Alternatively, you can select a single
word by double-clicking it, or select all of an editor's text by triple
clicking inside it. (See [Mouse Actions xix_ref_mouse.html].)

See also [Keyboard Shortcuts xix_ref_keys.html].

